name: UInterchangeSceneVariantSetsNode
doc: Class to represent a set of VariantSet nodes

methods.name: AddCustomVariantSetUid
methods.doc: Add the specified VariantSet's unique id to this object.

methods.name: GetCustomVariantSetUid
methods.doc: Retrieve the specified VariantSet's unique id for this object.

methods.name: GetCustomVariantSetUidCount
methods.doc: Retrieve the number of VariantSets for this object.

methods.name: GetCustomVariantSetUids
methods.doc: Retrieve all the VariantSets' unique ids for this object.

methods.name: RemoveCustomVariantSetUid
methods.doc: Remove the specified VariantSet's unique id from this object.
